### Attribute Min Max
// point wrangle

```C
float value;
float values[];
string attrname = "name";
float max_value;
float min_value;

for (int i=0; i<@numpt; i++)
{
	value = point(geoself(), attrname, i);
	append(values,value);
}

min_value = min(values);
max_value = max(values);

f[]@range;

@range[0] = min_value;
@range[1] = max_value;
```

